            "body": "Maybe yes, can I send you my lspconfig structure?\nFile plugins/lsp/lspconfig.lua\n```lua\nreturn {\n\t\"neovim/nvim-lspconfig\",\n\tevent = { \"BufReadPost\", \"BufNewFile\" },\n\tdependencies = {\n\t\t\"hrsh7th/cmp-nvim-lsp\",\n\t\t\"hrsh7th/nvim-cmp\",\n\t\t\"L3MON4D3/LuaSnip\",\n\t\t\"pmizio/typescript-tools.nvim\",\n\t\t{ \"folke/neodev.nvim\", opts = {} },\n\t},\n\tconfig = function()\n\t\tlocal path = \"/lua/amonteirom/plugins/lsp/langs/\"\n\n\t\tlocal lua = dofile(vim.fn.stdpath(\"config\") .. path .. \"lua.lua\")\n\t\tlua.luals()\n\n\t\tvim.diagnostic.config({\n\t\t\tvirtual_text = true,\n\t\t\tunderline = true,\n\t\t\tupdate_in_insert = true,\n\t\t\tseverity_sort = true,\n\t\t\tfloat = {\n\t\t\t\tborder = \"rounded\",\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t\tsigns = {\n\t\t\t\ttext = {\n\t\t\t\t\t[vim.diagnostic.severity.ERROR] = \"E\",\n\t\t\t\t\t[vim.diagnostic.severity.WARN] = \"W\",\n\t\t\t\t\t[vim.diagnostic.severity.HINT] = \"H\",\n\t\t\t\t\t[vim.diagnostic.severity.INFO] = \"I\",\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t})\n\n\t\t-- Configuração de handlers\n\t\tlocal handler_config = { border = \"rounded\" }\n\t\tvim.lsp.handlers[\"textDocument/hover\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.hover, handler_config)\n\t\tvim.lsp.handlers[\"textDocument/signatureHelp\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.signature_help, handler_config)\n\n```\n\nAnd in my file lsp/langs/lua.lua\n```lua\nlocal L = {}\nfunction L.luals()\n\tvim.lsp.config[\"luals\"] = {\n\t\tcmd = { \"lua-language-server\" },\n\t\tfiletypes = { \"lua\" },\n\t\troot_markers = { { \".luarc.json\", \".luarc.jsonc\" }, \".git\" },\n\t\tsettings = { Lua = { runtime = { version = \"LuaJIT\" } } },\n\t}\n\n\tvim.lsp.enable(\"luals\")\nend\n\nreturn L\n```\nAnd in my file lazy.lua ( chamado no init.lua )\n```lua\nlocal lazypath = vim.fn.stdpath(\"data\") .. \"/lazy/lazy.nvim\"\nif not vim.loop.fs_stat(lazypath) then\n\tvim.fn.system({\n\t\t\"git\",\n\t\t\"clone\",\n\t\t\"--filter=blob:none\",\n\t\t\"https://github.com/folke/lazy.nvim.git\",\n\t\t\"--branch=stable\",\n\t\tlazypath,\n\t})\nend\n\nvim.opt.rtp:prepend(lazypath)\n\nrequire(\"lazy\").setup({ { import = \"amonteirom.plugins\" }, { import = \"amonteirom.plugins.lsp\" } }, {\n\tchange_detection = {\n\t\tnotify = false,\n\t},\n})\n```",
